{"tid":735272,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"【小米上市】小米23日起納入恒生綜合指數　","createTime":"2018-07-09T10:51:10.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-09T12:12:57.000Z","uid":53379,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"e39669070043fd1d147c286ad4b37af21af6384e","tid":735272,"uid":53379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-09T10:51:10.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">【小米上市】小米23日起納入恒生綜合指數</span></strong>　<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.orangenews.hk/pic/0/10/16/39/10163925_826957.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.orangenews.hk%2Fpic%2F0%2F10%2F16%2F39%2F10163925_826957.png&h=ab571f1c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n恒生指數今日發佈公告稱，小米集團(01810)將於在7月20日收市後納入恒指，並於7月23日起生效。<br />\n<br />\n公告顯示，小米集團將被納入恒生綜合指數、恒生綜合行業指數&ndash;資訊科技業、恒生綜合大型股指數、恒生綜合大中型股指數、恒生環球綜合指數、恒生互聯網科技業指數。小米上市後，在10個交易日後便被納入恒生綜合指數，創下港股史上最快納入恒生綜合指數記錄。<br />\n<br />\n小米今日低開16.6元，高低位分別見17元及16元，全日收16.8元，較上市價17元，低20仙或1.2%，成交4.62億股，涉資76.82億元。<br />\n<br />\n對於今天的破發，雷軍現場表示，短期股價不是最重要的，長期價格是最重要的。「過去一個星期焦慮的是萬一跌的很難看，怎麼見人。小米過去8年又起有落，但特別順。這次IPO從低點開始，未必不是好事。最重要的是調整心態，把公司做好。完成定價之後的壓力才剛剛開始。我們還是要踏踏實實把公司做好，以經營做核心。繼續努力，繼續加油，把公司做好。」<br />\n<br />\n責編：陳正偉<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.orangenews.hk/finance/system/2018/07/09/010093928.shtml\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.orangenews.hk%2Ffinance%2Fsystem%2F2018%2F07%2F09%2F010093928.shtml&d=GVdTxnMf1sKUCcaeuRDk4E%2FDJpISyAq9ELy6OyFxwDc%3D&h=d9e0ceb3\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.orangenews.hk/finance/system/2018/07/09/010093928.shtml</a>"},{"pid":"cc321101325a4133d7f9fd00301e8b5498cb510c","tid":735272,"uid":53379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-09T10:53:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"abdb5141e4f56117230241d09f43a6630506ddde","tid":735272,"uid":4942,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-09T10:54:37.000Z","msg":"不是恆指 hsi"},{"pid":"0db54c90423162ae421a9902b9366579fbf52cb5","tid":735272,"uid":49918,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-09T10:56:30.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"013f9318ebcf90976705ba29570648341327f9bc","tid":735272,"uid":42820,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-09T10:58:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/09/185837_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F09%2F185837_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=c4ab7a29&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c5c8dd9aa4aa3593cf47f900506becd3ccd62ecf","tid":735272,"uid":177039,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"0db54c90423162ae421a9902b9366579fbf52cb5","tid":735272,"uid":49918,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-09T10:56:30.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-09T11:00:55.000Z","msg":"上市個下佢在場就知咩事啦 一間公司上市財爺走去做咩? 咪幫國家任務護航 <img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/09/190040_856a78b314be230abb82e11d560a1dbd.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F09%2F190040_856a78b314be230abb82e11d560a1dbd.gif&h=230a4a72&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a9c691ce666a26cac985036bd0b4c99da257dc7c","tid":735272,"uid":76310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0db54c90423162ae421a9902b9366579fbf52cb5","tid":735272,"uid":49918,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-09T10:56:30.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-09T11:02:05.000Z","msg":"因為凸手既親戚，你明的"},{"pid":"13390757582d2fdf6c8b7e182554941eb4060419","tid":735272,"uid":178619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-09T11:02:52.000Z","msg":"區區恆生綜合指數有咩implication? 咪又係海航樂視d fd<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 個liabilities睇下幾時爆"},{"pid":"8de5bec21e31b4338006bf59e6056dd3b397f33f","tid":735272,"uid":49918,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-09T11:03:23.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"43e6dcf8459a7bc9558db45ad636c6b30b1f5893","tid":735272,"uid":76310,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-09T11:04:10.000Z","msg":"揭開林鄭的意圖，能夠品嚐到這頭啖湯的真命天子，是已委聘上市保薦人磨拳擦掌搞上市的「小米」，若小米成功在香港以「同股不同權」方式掛牌，市值保守估計可達1,100億美元（8,500億港元），極可能成為今年最大的科網股集資，令小米變「大包米」。<br />\n<br />\n林鄭今次大開中門，本刊發現，原來林鄭一直與小米金主「啟明創投」關係密切。啟明的老闆之一梁頴宇，其父母是前立法會議員梁劉柔芬與足總主席梁孔德，多年來不單與林鄭在公事上互相扶持，私下關係更加密切。小米若成功上市，將帶挈「啟明創投」大撈一筆。<br />\n<br />\n而林鄭大兒子林節思早在「升呢」入小米做營運經理之前，亦曾在啟明做實習生；林鄭出手，再為大仔在小米打開了上位方便之門。"},{"pid":"879a3001b73c9ce64e3ac99c3f54c61a1f59a644","tid":735272,"uid":76310,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-09T11:04:57.000Z","msg":"咁快入恒指<br />\n唔係有人造手腳，會咁快咩"},{"pid":"d96a7c007be74bbb213198be6e2b3ab22ebce05d","tid":735272,"uid":76310,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-09T11:08:22.000Z","msg":"點解入恒指？<br />\n<br />\n因為係指數就乜叉港股基金，香港指數基金，盈富，中港指數基金，指數基金都會買佢<br />\n<br />\n小米上市後，在10個交易日後便被納入恒生綜合指數，創下港股史上最快納入恒生綜合指數記錄。<br />\n<br />\n快到。當年國家個親生仔中移動都無咁快入藍籌。香港是人治社會，明顯到弱智都知"},{"pid":"5fe4e12ef785d73c6f003bdb9e5c2f331c42d5c1","tid":735272,"uid":106247,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-09T11:08:35.000Z","msg":"又想連累恆指跌多d<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nall in 熊對沖返<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"49789f3fc3df6c1dbfd5a0b40dee17e4ccd3d617","tid":735272,"uid":192589,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-09T11:09:22.000Z","msg":"23日有$10蚊當佢贏"},{"pid":"83f6b15322743ee024cce907106f675725f32d17","tid":735272,"uid":1654,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-09T11:09:55.000Z","msg":"蝕錢照上市、入恒指，睇黎係下隻700"},{"pid":"338b37775831a96b9ac810dd899d9d235a46b54f","tid":735272,"uid":2230,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"879a3001b73c9c